    "content": "Marc Anthony\r\nSong:  You sang to me \r\nAlbum: Marc Anthony\r\n\r\nBASS-LINE through out verses and chorus: (A\u2260 \u2013 A\u2260 \u2013 G \u2013 G \u2013 D\u2260 \u2013 F \u2013 A\u2260 \u2013 F) \r\n\r\n[INTRO]:  Instrumental   \r\n\r\nPart I: 00:22  ---  Bass-line:( A\u2260 \u2013 A\u2260 \u2013 G \u2013 G \u2013 D\u2260 \u2013 D\u2260 \u2013 F \u2013 F )\r\n\r\n[tab]G|--------10-10--------10~-|--------10-10--------10~-|-\r\nD|---8~-8-------8--8-8-----|---8~-8-------8--8-8-----|- A\u2260 \u2013 A\u2260\r\nA|-x-----------------------|-8-----------------------|- \r\nE|-------------------------|-------------------------|-[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------------------|-----------------------------|-\r\nD|----------12-12-----------12~|----------12-12-----------12~|-\r\nA|-8/10~-10-------10--10-10----|---10~-10-------10--10-10----|- G \u2013 G\r\nE|-----------------------------|-10--------------------------|-[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------------|-----------------------|-\r\nD|--------8-8---------8~-|--------8-8---------8~-|-\r\nA|-8\\6~-6-----6--6-6-----|---6~-6-----6--6-6-----|- D\u2260 \u2013 D\u2260\r\nE|-----------------------|-6---------------------|-[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------------|-------------------------||-\r\nD|-----------------------|--------10-10--------10~-||-\r\nA|--------8-8---------8~-|---8~-8-------8--8-8-----||- F \u2013 F\r\nE|-8\\6~-6-----6--6-6-----|-6-----------------------||-[/tab]\r\n\r\nPart II: 00:22 --- Bass-line: ( A\u2260 \u2013 A\u2260 \u2013 G \u2013 G \u2013 D\u2260 \u2013 F \u2013 A\u2260 \u2013 F )\r\n                             \r\n[tab]G|--------10-10--------10~-|--------10-10--------10~-|-\r\nD|---8~-8-------8--8-8-----|---8~-8-------8--8-8-----|-\r\nA|-x-----------------------|-8-----------------------|- A\u2260 \u2013 A\u2260\r\nE|-------------------------|-------------------------|-[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------------------|-----------------------------|-\r\nD|----------12-12-----------12~|----------12-12-----------12~|-\r\nA|-8/10~-10-------10--10-10----|---10~-10-------10--10-10----|- G \u2013 G\r\nE|-----------------------------|-10--------------------------|-[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------------|-------------------------|-\r\nD|--------8-8---------8~-|--------10-10--------10~-|-\r\nA|-8\\6~-6-----6--6-6-----|---8~-8-------8--8-8-----|- D\u2260 \u2013 F\r\nE|-----------------------|-6-----------------------|-[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------------|-------------------------||-\r\nD|-----------------------|--------10-10--------10~-||-\r\nA|--------8-8---------8~-|---8~-8-------8--8-8-----||-    \u2013 F\r\nE|-8\\6~-6-----6--6-6-----|-6-----------------------||- A\u2260  [/tab]\r\n\r\n                         Ooooh\r\n\r\n\r\n[Verse 1]: 00:45 --- Bass-line: (A\u2260 \u2013 A\u2260 \u2013 G \u2013 G \u2013 D\u2260 \u2013 F \u2013 A\u2260 \u2013 F)\r\n\r\n[tab]G|--------10-10--------10~-|--------10-10--------10~-|-\r\nD|---8~-8-------8--8-8-----|---8~-8-------8--8-8-----|-\r\nA|-x-----------------------|-8-----------------------|- A\u2260 \u2013 A\u2260\r\nE|-------------------------|-------------------------|-\r\nI just wanted you to comfort me\r\nWhen I called you late last night you see[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------------------|-----------------------------|-\r\nD|----------12-12-----------12~|----------12-12-----------12~|-\r\nA|-8/10~-10-------10--10-10----|---10~-10-------10--10-10----|- G \u2013 G\r\nE|-----------------------------|-10--------------------------|-\r\nI was fallin' into love\r\nYes, I was crashin' into love[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------------|-------------------------|-\r\nD|--------8-8---------8~-|--------10-10--------10~-|-\r\nA|-8\\6~-6-----6--6-6-----|---8~-8-------8--8-8-----|- D\u2260 \u2013 F\r\nE|-----------------------|-6-----------------------|-\r\nOh of all the words you sang to me\r\nAbout life, the truth and being free, yeah[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------------|-------------------------||-\r\nD|-----------------------|--------10-10--------10~-||-\r\nA|--------8-8---------8~-|---8~-8-------8--8-8-----||-    \u2013 F\r\nE|-8\\6~-6-----6--6-6-----|-6-----------------------||- A\u2260  \r\n   C                      G\r\nYou sang to me, oh how you sang to me[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[Verse 2]: 01:08 --- Bass-line: ( A\u2260 \u2013 A\u2260 \u2013 G \u2013 G \u2013 D\u2260 \u2013 F \u2013 A\u2260 \u2013 F )\r\n\r\n       A\u2260\r\nGirl, I live for how you make me feel\r\nA\u2260 \r\nSo I question all this being real\r\n         G\r\n'Cause I'm not afraid to love\r\nG \r\nFor the first time I'm not afraid of love\r\n    D\u2260\r\nThis day seems made for you and me\r\nF \r\nAnd you showed me what life needs to be\r\n         A\u2260                 F\r\nYeah, you sang to me, oh you sang to me\r\n\r\n\r\n[Chorus]:01:32 --- Bassline: ( A\u2260 \u2013 A\u2260 \u2013 G \u2013 G \u2013 D\u2260 \u2013 F \u2013 A\u2260 \u2013 F )\r\n\r\n[tab]\u201cPart I\u201d\r\nG|--------10-10--------10~-|--------10-10--------10~-|-\r\nD|---8~-8-------8--8-8-----|---8~-8-------8--8-8-----|-\r\nA|-x-----------------------|-8-----------------------|- A\u2260 \u2013 A\u2260\r\nE|-------------------------|-------------------------|-\r\n       A\u2260                               \r\nAll the while you were in front of me I never realized[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------------------|-----------------------------|-\r\nD|----------12-12-----------12~|----------12-12-----------12~|-\r\nA|-8/10~-10-------10--10-10----|---10~-10-------10--10-10----|- G \u2013 G\r\nE|-----------------------------|-10--------------------------|-\r\n     G\r\nI just can't believe I didn't see it in your eyes[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------------|-------------------------|-\r\nD|--------8-8---------8~-|--------10-10--------10~-|-\r\nA|-8\\6~-6-----6--6-6-----|---8~-8-------8--8-8-----|- D\u2260 \u2013 F\r\nE|-----------------------|-6-----------------------|-\r\n        D\u2260        